1.10	Chocolate_(2005_film)	Chocolate (2005 film)	Chocolate is a 2005 Bollywood film starring Anil Kapoor, Sunil Shetty, Arshad Warsi, Emraan Hashmi, Irrfan Khan, Tanushree Dutta and Sushma Reddy in the lead roles. It is a thriller and most part of the film was shot in London. The film is an unofficial remake of the Hollywood movie The Usual Suspects.	
